      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engagement, featuring the robust 3.8L DFI flat-six mated to a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is sharpened by Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a factory-spec limited-slip differential, ensuring neutral handling and exceptional turn-in bite. Meticulously maintained with a flawless DME over-rev report, the mechanicals are in peak operating condition with no signs of bore scoring or typical AOS issues. Finished with cross-drilled rotors and a sport-tuned exhaust, this example offers a visceral, analog driving experience that remains uncompromised by age or wear.",
