      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that has been maintained with obsessive care. This car is in showroom condition, having been stored exclusively in a climate-controlled garage and hand-washed to preserve its flawless factory finish. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections of any kind. The alloy wheels are pristine, free of any curb rash, and are wrapped in premium tires with near-full tread depth. Inside, the cabin is immaculate and smoke-free; the leather upholstery is supple with no visible wear or bolster compression, and the carpets have been protected by heavy-duty mats since day one. Every technological feature, from the infotainment system to the advanced driver assists, operates with precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history documented at certified intervals. Most recently, it underwent a full multi-point inspection and fluid service to ensure it drives exactly as it did when it first left the assembly line. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a peak-condition vehicle for the discerning enthusiast.",
